        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " spoken of by Festus does not mean his own judicial inquiry, though it is so used once in Polybius (6. 16:2), but the disputes or discussions on such subjects as the Resurrection, etc. (",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
