        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Titus 3:9",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), in which Festus felt himself at a loss. The A.V., therefore, expresses the sense more nearly than the R.V. The T.R. too, which inserts ",
        "children": []
